title: Beautiful 1x1! Come apply!
posting_body: ['Jasmine Park Apartments in Pasadena, TX, offers spacious 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartment homes.', 'Located in the heart of the Pasadena district, Jasmine Park Apartments is just minutes from Beltway 8, I-45, Hwy.', '225, major employers, medical facilities, Pasadena schools, and numerous shopping and dining opportunities.', 'Call today to learn more and to schedule your community tour.', '-Hablamos Espanol', '-Great Schools', '-Updated Interiors', '-Refreshing Pool', '-On-Site Maintenance Team', '-Outdoor Social Space', '-Professional and Friendly Management', '-Close to Shopping, Dining + Entertainment', '-Private Balconies']
